{"id":276917,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/李开复：78条冤死的微博/","date":"2013-01-30T00:04:27Z","modified":"2013-01-30T00:04:27Z","title":"李开复：78条冤死的微博","content":"<p>昨日，创新工场董事长兼CEO李开复在新浪微博贴出了自己过去6个月被删除的78条微博截图。截止发稿时，该条微博已有4千7百多条转发和3千多条评论：</p>\n<p>@李开复：【冤死的微博】过去6个月，我发的微博一共被删除78条（见图）。大家评评理：这78条，真的那么该死吗？</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/likaifu2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-276918\" title=\"likaifu2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/likaifu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"566\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/likaifu2.jpg 566w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/likaifu2-300x198.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 566px) 100vw, 566px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-276919\" title=\"李开复1\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"437\" height=\"9870\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-276921\" title=\"李开复3\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"430\" height=\"5141\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复3.jpg 430w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复3-25x300.jpg 25w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-276920\" title=\"李开复2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/01/李开复2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"431\" height=\"4231\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[8859,14328,8616]}